{
  "stem": "18186.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 23.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, I told him I have a boyfriend-- I have a boyfriend, and then he became a husband.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I-- by the time the papers came, that I had everything there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I had a baby.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, first of all to him, I can't come with-- by myself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I have a boyfriend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I write him, that I got married.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It took so long.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was like a couple years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were married in-- in-- '46.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were-- we came to the United States, it was '49, a few years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So-- and that was-- that's the way it happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And don't ask me why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I really don't-- cannot explain it to you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, survivors.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some lived-- we stayed in the community.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And other people lived outside the community, like in private homes, private apartments, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all this the UNRRA took care.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they gives us some money sometimes and this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A little, here and there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, my husband was a policeman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For the community, for this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, just for that little house, it was one house or so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I really-- I just survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just it was I was one of the lucky ones.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my-- my sister and brothers were there, and they didn't do that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or maybe they did and they caught them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's something I never know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then I met people like after-- years later, we met people from Israel, when I went in '63, and they told me that they find out that this one, my brother they caught-- my brother going on the way-- going to Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they killed him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my mother was killed someplace else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But this is all talk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And nobody saw it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
